OL,3,CIs this the real face of Anne Boleyn?
OL,4,CScientists uncover sketch using AI
OL,6,FScientists say they have used facial
OL,7,Frecognition technology to find what
OL,8,Fthey believe to be the first picture
OL,9,Fof Anne Boleyn drawn during her
OL,10,Flifetime, but some art historians are
OL,11,Fsceptical - ITV News Reporter Aisha
OL,12,FZahid has more
OL,14,FAnne Boleyn is one of the most famous
OL,15,Fqueens of England's history, playing
OL,16,Fpivotal role as catalyst of the
OL,17,FEnglish Reformation ` and being the
OL,18,Ffirst of Henry the VIII's wives to
OL,19,Flose her head.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
