OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777770201
OL,3,CIs this the real face of Anne Boleyn?
OL,4,CScientists uncover sketch using AI
OL,6,FDespite her fame historians have never
OL,7,Fbeen sure what she actually looked
OL,8,Flike, as every confirmed portrait is
OL,9,Fthought to have been painted after her
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FNow, scientists from the University of
OL,13,FBradford say they have used facial
OL,14,Frecognition technology to find a
OL,15,Fsketch that could really be her.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
