CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777770201
OL,3,CIs this the real face of Anne Boleyn?
OL,4,CScientists uncover sketch using AI
OL,6,FUsing facial recognition, contemporary
OL,7,Fdocumentary evidence, and a newly
OL,8,Fproposed "AI-driven Working Likeness
OL,9,FMethodology", the research team say
OL,10,Fthey have found a match among sketches
OL,11,Fin the Royal Collection.
OL,13,FThey say a drawing by German painter
OL,14,FHans Holbein the Younger, currently
OL,15,Flabelled "An Unidentified Woman",
OL,16,Faligns far more closely with
OL,17,Feyewitness descriptions, family
OL,18,Fresemblance networks, and
OL,19,Fcomputational analysis than other
OL,20,Fworks long-accepted to be of Boleyn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
