PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777770201
OL,3,CIs this the real face of Anne Boleyn?
OL,4,CScientists uncover sketch using AI
OL,6,F"We essentially ran facial recognition
OL,7,Facross the entire corpus of Hans
OL,8,FHolbein, and when we actually look at
OL,9,Fall this together, looking at family
OL,10,Fclustering, the unidentified woman
OL,11,Fseems to cluster with the royal
OL,12,Ffamily," said Hassan Ugail, professor
OL,13,Fof visual computing.
OL,15,F"We think it might take the place of
OL,16,FAnne Boleyn," he added.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
