PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777770201
OL,3,CIs this the real face of Anne Boleyn?
OL,4,CScientists uncover sketch using AI
OL,6,FNot everyone is convinced, however,
OL,7,Fwith art historian Dr Bendor Grosvenor
OL,8,Ftelling ITV News: "They're trying to
OL,9,Ftake a 21st century technology, which
OL,10,Fis facial recognition and AI, and
OL,11,Fassume that it can just be put
OL,12,Fimmediately back onto drawings and
OL,13,Fartworks made 500 years earlier in the
OL,14,F16th century.
OL,16,F"The methodology here is so profoundly
OL,17,Fmisplaced that it almost is impossible
OL,18,Ffor it to get off the ground in the
OL,19,Ffirst place."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
